Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.50,0:00:03.98,Standard,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's start with today's first request.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.02,0:00:12.52,Standard,,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact, this time, we've received the same request from various people all over the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.52,0:00:14.58,Standard,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Sawabe-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.58,0:00:16.94,Standard,,0,0,0,,Something really unexpected happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.94,0:00:23.86,Standard,,0,0,0,,So, in case you didn't know ... at TV Tokyo, in a show called "Why did you come to Japan?" ...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.92,0:00:28.38,Standard,,0,0,0,,...they talked to a 19y/o German couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.38,0:00:32.34,Standard,,0,0,0,,It turns out they were huge fans of Tantei Knight Scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:38.88,Standard,,0,0,0,,So they came all the way from Germany to see Knight Scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.48,0:00:43.68,Standard,,0,0,0,,Just to see Knight Scoop?\N - Yes, just for that purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.68,0:00:47.44,Standard,,0,0,0,,So did they make it to a taping?\N - Well, it was a spontaneous trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.50,0:00:57.58,Standard,,0,0,0,,They came over without knowing anything about the application process, so when they arrived at the recording studio, they weren't able to get inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.66,0:01:05.70,Standard,,0,0,0,,Now after the broadcast, Knight Scoop fans were thinking: "Why don't you invite these fans?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.70,0:01:09.76,Standard,,0,0,0,,And that's when we started receiving requests from people all over the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.76,0:01:13.98,Standard,,0,0,0,,So I, Detective Sawabe, took on the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.98,0:01:18.80,Standard,,0,0,0,,Whether they were still in Japan, and whether I was able to find them - please take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:23.00,Standard,,0,0,0,,Something strange has been happening, take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.00,0:01:26.30,Standard,,0,0,0,,These are all requests! Strange, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:32.80,Standard,,0,0,0,,We were flooded by clients, so I'm wondering where we should go from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.80,0:01:36.78,Standard,,0,0,0,,We should pay TV Tokyo a visit first of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.50,0:01:45.88,Standard,,0,0,0,,Here we are, we've arrived at TV Tokyo! Shall we head inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.10,0:01:50.70,Standard,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, we're with Tantei Knight Scoop ...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.70,0:01:54.70,Standard,,0,0,0,,Where would I find the staff members of "Why did you come ...?"\N - This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.70,0:01:57.18,Standard,,0,0,0,,This is their staff room?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:02:00.48,Standard,,0,0,0,,It looks like a changing room at the beach...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.54,0:02:02.80,Standard,,0,0,0,,They're completeley isolated for that show.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.38,0:02:09.44,Standard,,0,0,0,,I contacted you some time ago, yes? Ah, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.64,0:02:11.48,Standard,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:15.96,Standard,,0,0,0,,The German couple you interviewed, they said they really liked Knight Scoop, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.96,0:02:21.78,Standard,,0,0,0,,Is there a chance you could show us the clip where they said they flew over for that purpose?\N - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.10,0:02:24.60,Standard,,0,0,0,,So it's these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:27.76,Standard,,0,0,0,,Konnichiha!\N - Why did you come to Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.26,0:02:36.74,Standard,,0,0,0,,It's really funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.10,0:02:39.84,Standard,,0,0,0,,That's lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:44.20,Standard,,0,0,0,,They'd never expect we'd be watching this together with a Detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:12.14,Standard,,0,0,0,,Would it be ok if we came along?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:19.78,Standard,,0,0,0,,They're something else, huh? Even as {\i1}otaku{\i0}, they're really something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:21.68,Standard,,0,0,0,,Osaka, konnichiha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.94,0:03:26.02,Standard,,0,0,0,,By the way, have you scheduled an appointment or anything like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.02,0:03:27.82,Standard,,0,0,0,,{\pos(485.333,214)\fs36}Now! Off to ABC TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:29.74,Standard,,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.74,0:03:33.18,Standard,,0,0,0,,They're not even taping today in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.28,0:03:35.10,Standard,,0,0,0,,{\pos(136,381.11)\fs20}They seem really \Ndesolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.70,0:03:38.34,Standard,,0,0,0,,Ah~, this is heartbreaking to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.34,0:03:39.78,Standard,,0,0,0,,That's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:46.78,Standard,,0,0,0,,ABC, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:48.18,Standard,,0,0,0,,How adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:49.86,Standard,,0,0,0,,{\pos(465.778,222)}Next, they revisited memorable locations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:51.40,Standard,,0,0,0,,{\pos(488.889,379.333)\fs28}Arrived at Nara Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:04.22,Standard,,0,0,0,,So they went to places like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:07.48,Standard,,0,0,0,,It's like they're on a pilgrimage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:23.70,Standard,,0,0,0,,How happy they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:30.84,Standard,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\pos(140.445,383.778)}They're reenacting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:42.28,Standard,,0,0,0,,{\fs28\pos(474.666,383.778)}Respect for the Detectives!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.54,0:04:43.94,Standard,,0,0,0,,That means a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:49.72,Standard,,0,0,0,,Somehow, I'm also really moved by this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:53.68,Standard,,0,0,0,,When did you film this?\N - Around the first half of April.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:57.04,Standard,,0,0,0,,In other words, they're still in Japan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:04:59.62,Standard,,0,0,0,,They might be, just barely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:04.66,Standard,,0,0,0,,Do you have an idea where we could find them? - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.66,0:05:07.32,Standard,,0,0,0,,We can try.  - Is that ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.92,0:05:11.00,Standard,,0,0,0,,But ... but ... I can't speak English well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:13.44,Standard,,0,0,0,,You're useless as a director!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.52,0:05:16.40,Standard,,0,0,0,,If they've left already, then we're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.52,0:05:18.96,Standard,,0,0,0,,{\pos(475.556,222)\fs28}5 minutes later ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.10,0:05:21.24,Standard,,0,0,0,,I reached someone. - You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:26.44,Standard,,0,0,0,,It seems they've been staying at a hotel in the Ueno / Asakusa area.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:34.60,Standard,,0,0,0,,I asked them if they could meet with us again and didn't mention anything about Tantei Knight Scoop. I thought it might be a nice surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:41.16,Standard,,0,0,0,,Aaah, you're amazing! That'll be fun to see when they find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:43.64,Standard,,0,0,0,,{\fs28\pos(490.666,214)}Heading to the hotel where they are staying ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.64,0:05:47.88,Standard,,0,0,0,,One of the staff members just went inside the hotel ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:53.76,Standard,,0,0,0,,... and she should come out with the two of them in a bit. They still don't know that we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:06:00.52,Standard,,0,0,0,,Ah, they're coming, they're here, ahh~, it's them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:03.66,Standard,,0,0,0,,How about we go see them in person?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:09.90,Standard,,0,0,0,,Ah, excuse me. Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:12.00,Standard,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:18.94,Standard,,0,0,0,,You've been doing an interview, thinking it was for "Why did you come to Japan?", so why did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:32.48,Standard,,0,0,0,,You've cut your hair so much, I almost didn't recognize you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:36.08,Standard,,0,0,0,,We came to meet you!\N - Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:38.94,Standard,,0,0,0,,Knight Scoop has been getting so many requests because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.28,0:06:42.60,Standard,,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:44.78,Standard,,0,0,0,,Look how nice they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:48.54,Standard,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling right now?\N - Very nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:53.50,Standard,,0,0,0,,Now because last time didn't work out, you'll finally be able to see Knight Scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:55.34,Standard,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:07:06.26,Standard,,0,0,0,,Sawabe-san~\N - You even know my name? Wow! I'm really glad! I'm known in Germany!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:09.10,Standard,,0,0,0,,So, do you have some time to spare today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:12.82,Standard,,0,0,0,,So how about we head out together?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.90,0:07:24.02,Standard,,0,0,0,,For the two who've come to love Tantei Knight Scoop: W・E・L・C・O・M・E
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:31.28,Standard,,0,0,0,,So as a matter of fact, it so happens that Takeyama-san is also filming in Tokyo today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:39.34,Standard,,0,0,0,,We're going to head over now and surprise Detective Takeyama at his shooting location.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:43.00,Standard,,0,0,0,,The weather is really nice today, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:44.52,Standard,,0,0,0,,{\pos(480,359.778)\fs28}We didn't tell Detective Takeyama anything about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:48.18,Standard,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.24,0:07:53.20,Standard,,0,0,0,,He, he, he!\N- Konnichiha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:55.20,Standard,,0,0,0,,Do you recognize them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.46,0:07:56.88,Standard,,0,0,0,,They're famous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:03.08,Standard,,0,0,0,,You know about TV Tokyo's "Why did you come to Japan?", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:10.94,Standard,,0,0,0,,They said that they really liked Tantei Knight Scoop.\N - Ah, I've heard there was someone like that! - That's them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:15.72,Standard,,0,0,0,,You?! What did you come for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:19.54,Standard,,0,0,0,,Hello! I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:23.84,Standard,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.84,0:08:27.28,Standard,,0,0,0,,So on Friday, they'll attend a taping.\N - Ah, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.28,0:08:29.96,Standard,,0,0,0,,Fantastic! - We're really glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.96,0:08:32.58,Standard,,0,0,0,,What was it you called the director again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:37.22,Standard,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.22,0:08:40.38,Standard,,0,0,0,,So ... do you have some more time left?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.26,0:08:44.94,Standard,,0,0,0,,Then, should we go to Osaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:47.46,Standard,,0,0,0,,{\fs28\pos(480,149.111)}To Osaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:49.48,Standard,,0,0,0,,We've arrived in Osaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.48,0:08:51.86,Standard,,0,0,0,,Osaka, konnichiha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:53.94,Standard,,0,0,0,,Do you know Tsutenkaku Tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:59.24,Standard,,0,0,0,,Then how about we go there now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:05.92,Standard,,0,0,0,,Are there any other people you know, Detectives or otherwise? - Hayashi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:10.62,Standard,,0,0,0,,Oh I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:17.14,Standard,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's a place you know, look - Tsutenkaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.42,0:09:27.94,Standard,,0,0,0,,Do you recognize him? Nonoyama-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.82,0:09:37.00,Standard,,0,0,0,,Seems like he's really popular with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.00,0:09:43.44,Standard,,0,0,0,,Actually, he's come all the way from Nagoya for you.\N - Really? Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.44,0:09:45.90,Standard,,0,0,0,,Isn't there something you want to show them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:53.80,Standard,,0,0,0,,Next I'll make it fly using telekinesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:10:00.04,Standard,,0,0,0,,What a mysterious thing to be shown!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:02.18,Standard,,0,0,0,,{\fs28\pos(487.111,208.667)}That's all from Nonoyama-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:08.90,Standard,,0,0,0,,So we've arrived all the way at the top. Here, you can scream out whatever you're feeling right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.10,0:10:20.68,Standard,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy, because we get to see Knight Scoop live!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:32.70,Standard,,0,0,0,,Seeing their eyes light up like this makes me really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:39.02,Standard,,0,0,0,,But we're not done yet, there's one more place I want to show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:41.38,Standard,,0,0,0,,{\fs28\pos(480,211.333)}Off to another place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:44.12,Standard,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you'll enjoy this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:47.98,Standard,,0,0,0,,We've made it, this way please. It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:07.56,Standard,,0,0,0,,Konnichiha, Hayashi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.62,0:11:09.96,Standard,,0,0,0,,Hayashi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:16.60,Standard,,0,0,0,,What's going on here? You gave me a call but I still don't know what this is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.60,0:11:20.26,Standard,,0,0,0,,Hello. - Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.42,0:11:22.08,Standard,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:27.02,Standard,,0,0,0,,So they came from Germany because they wanted to see Knight Scoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.02,0:11:32.04,Standard,,0,0,0,,They liked it so much, they decided to come to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:43.66,Standard,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second, I should have some ...\N - He told us to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,0:11:47.58,Standard,,0,0,0,,These were returned for a different purpose.\N - Made by the sensei himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:50.36,Standard,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:56.98,Standard,,0,0,0,,Hayashi-sensei, it seems you have the presence of an idol! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.12,0:11:59.92,Standard,,0,0,0,,Those look delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:07.64,Standard,,0,0,0,,So good! - It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:12.04,Standard,,0,0,0,,You're a good chef.\N - I'm a good chef? Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.78,0:12:17.96,Standard,,0,0,0,,So today, in very short time, we've visited a lot of places...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:24.54,Standard,,0,0,0,,So even when you return to Germany, will you continue to watch Knight Scoop?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.82,0:12:34.68,Standard,,0,0,0,,And something we thought was just right for you to have when you return home ... the DVD box!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.98,0:12:47.12,Standard,,0,0,0,,Let's also become Detectives!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:52.72,Standard,,0,0,0,,{\fs28\pos(248.889,120.666)}And then, their dream finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.30,0:12:52.72,Standard,,0,0,0,,{\fs28\pos(768.889,291.333)}... comes true
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:12.78,Standard,,0,0,0,,Their dream has come true! They've made it to a taping!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:15.82,Standard,,0,0,0,,Now that your dream has come true, how do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:31.28,Standard,,0,0,0,,Looks like you've made the director cry. Cry-guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:40.06,Standard,,0,0,0,,What's it like, seeing Cry-guy in person?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.48,0:13:55.04,Standard,,0,0,0,,I'm deeply moved, so thank you.\N - You're all so funny!

